comment: LaVine (MIN) makes contact with Gordon's (NOP) arm that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Cunningham (NOP) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Rubio's (MIN) drive to the basket.
Cunningham (NOP) makes contact with Wiggins' (MIN) body that affects his shot attempt.
Wiggins (MIN) makes incidental contact with Holiday (NOP) away from the ball. RATR.
Dieng (MIN) makes contact with Gordon (NOP) that affects his RSBQ at the start of his drive.
Dieng (MIN) makes incidental contact with Anderson (NOP) that does not affect his FOM.
Gordon (NOP) does not establish a legal guarding position prior to the contact with Wiggins (MIN) on his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the crew determined that Gordon (NOP) was outside the restricted area, but was not in a legal guarding position. The block call was upheld.
